Class CefSchemeHandlerCallback

CefBase

   +--CefSchemeHandlerCallback
   in cef_scheme.h
class CefSchemeHandlerCallback
extends CefBase

Class used to facilitate asynchronous responses to custom scheme handler requests. The methods of this class may be called on any thread.
